        <title>买卖股票的最佳时机：从贪心到状态机</title>
        <link>https://skylm808.github.io/p/%E4%B9%B0%E5%8D%96%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%BA%E4%BB%8E%E8%B4%AA%E5%BF%83%E5%88%B0%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E6%9C%BA/</link>
